### taoist

[说明]
    *) 准备: 
             python -m venv .venv
             source .venv/bin/activate
             pip install -r requirements.txt
    *) 打包: 
             make
    *) 安装: 
             mkdir /opt/taoist
             pip install taoist-0.0.1-py3-none-any.whl -t /opt/taoist
    *) 运行:
             bash manage.sh up
    *) 清理: 
             make clean
